public class PdfController : Controller\n   {\n       [HttpPost]\n       public ActionResult Upload(HttpPostedFileBase file)\n       {\n           if (file != null && file.ContentLength > 0)\n           {\n               PdfToHtmlConverter converter = new PdfToHtmlConverter();\n               converter.UploadAndConvertPdf(file);\n\n               // You might want to return the HTML content or a success message\n               return Content("PDF converted to HTML successfully.");\n           }\n\n           return Content("No file uploaded.");\n       }\n   }